com.crawljax.condition.eventablecondition
Class EventableCondition

java.lang.Object
  com.crawljax.condition.eventablecondition.EventableCondition

public class EventableCondition
extends Object

An EventableCondition specifies properties of an eventable which should be satisfied in order to crawl the element. The user does not need this class when using the API. Only for use with properties files .
